UNITED STATES of America, Appellant, v. Myron J. CLIFFORD, Appellee. No. 7599. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. Aug. 29, 1934. Peirson M. Hall, U. S. Atty., of Los Angeles, Cal. Mooney & Hoffman, of Los Angeles, Cal., for appellee.

Before WILBUR and SAWTELLE, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Upon stipulation of counsel for the respective parties, ordered appeal dismissed; mandate forthwith.
